title: Jack Mohr
text: Jack Mohr (11 July 1906 – 7 June 1971) was an <a href="Australian%20rules%20football">Australian rules football</a>er who played with <a href="St%20Kilda%20Football%20Club">St Kilda</a> in the <a href="Victorian%20Football%20League%20%281897%E2%80%931989%29">Victorian Football League</a> (VFL).
